# Gemini AI API key — REQUIRED for the Cal AI assistant.
#
# 1. Create a key at: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
# 2. Copy this file to `.env` and paste your key below.
# 3. Restart the dev server (Vite only reads .env at startup).
#
# NOTE: The `VITE_` prefix is mandatory — Vite only exposes prefixed vars
# to the client. WARNING: any VITE_ var is bundled into the public
# JavaScript and is visible to anyone who opens the deployed site.
# For production, proxy Gemini calls through a backend so the key stays secret.
VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY="MY_GEMINI_API_KEY"
